'''羅伯特·克拉克·席格'''（{{lang-en|Robert Clark Seger}}，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|s|iː|g|ər}}，{{bd|1945年|5月6日||}}）是美國歌手、詞曲作家和音樂家。作為一名在[[底特律|底特律]]小有成就的藝人，席格在1960年代以'''Bob Seger and the Last Heard'''或'''Bob Seger System'''的名義表演並錄製作品，從他的1968年首張專輯《{{link-en|Ramblin' Gamblin' Man}}》開始（裡面的{{link-en|Ramblin' Gamblin' Man (歌曲)|Ramblin' Gamblin' Man (song)|同名歌曲}}成為了他的第一首熱門歌曲）。到了1970年代早期，他開始獨用藝名Bob Seger並去掉其它後綴，並於1973年召集一群底特律的樂手組成'''銀彈合唱團'''（{{lang-en|The Silver Bullet Band}}）。三年後，席格與銀彈合唱團於1975年在{{link-en|TCF中心|TCF Center|柯柏大廳}}的現場錄音專輯《{{link-en|Live Bullet}}》讓他們在國內獲得了重大成功，而同年（1976年）的專輯《{{link-en|Night Moves (專輯)|Night Moves (album)|Night Moves}}》更讓他們成為國際大名。席格經常與[[亚拉巴马州|阿拉巴馬州]]的{{link-en|馬斯爾肖爾斯節奏聲部樂團|Muscle Shoals Rhythm Section}}合作錄製不少的熱銷歌曲與專輯。

席格有著沙啞而強力的歌聲，而他圍繞於[[愛|愛]]、[[女性|女人]]和[[藍領|藍領階級]]主題的歌曲更是{{link-en|中心地帶搖滾|Heartland rock}}的標準範例。他擁有不少熱門歌曲，如〈{{link-en|Night Moves (歌曲)|Night Moves (song)|Night Moves}}〉、〈{{link-en|Turn the Page (巴布·席格歌曲)|Turn the Page (Bob Seger song)|Turn the Page}}〉、〈{{link-en|Still the Same (巴布·席格歌曲)|Still the Same (Bob Seger song)|Still the Same}}〉、〈{{link-en|We've Got Tonite}}〉、〈{{link-en|Against the Wind (巴布·席格歌曲)|Against the Wind (Bob Seger song)|Against the Wind}}〉、〈{{link-en|You'll Accomp'ny Me}}〉、〈{{link-en|Hollywood Nights}}〉、〈{{link-en|Shame on the Moon}}〉、〈{{link-en|Like a Rock (歌曲)|Like a Rock (song)|Like a Rock}}〉和為1987年電影《{{link-en|比佛利山超級警探2|Beverly Hills Cop II}}》所創作的〈{{link-en|Shakedown (巴布·席格歌曲)|Shakedown (Bob Seger song)|Shakedown}}〉，後者更在[[告示牌百强单曲榜|《告示牌》百大單曲榜]]上登冠。席格也合寫了[[老鹰_(乐队)|老鷹樂團]]的冠軍單曲〈{{link-en|Heartache Tonight}}〉，而席格自己的歌〈{{link-en|Old Time Rock and Roll}}〉被[[美國唱片業協會|美國唱片業協會]]名列於「{{link-en|世紀金曲|Songs of the Century}}」榜單中。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://davesmusicdatabase.blogspot.com/2012/03/riaaneas-top-365-songs-of-20th-century.html|title=Dave's Music Database: The RIAA/NEA's Top 365 Songs of the 20th Century|first=Dave|last=Whitaker|website=Davesmusicdatabase.blogspot.com|date=2001-03-07|accessdate=2020-09-13|archive-date=2012-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120524080250/http://davesmusicdatabase.blogspot.com/2012/03/riaaneas-top-365-songs-of-20th-century.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

席格的事業跨越六十年、在全球銷售超過七千五百萬張唱片，讓他變成[[暢銷音樂藝人列表|世界上最暢銷的音樂藝人]]之一。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.pjstar.com/news/20180918/bob-seger-coming-to-peoria-civic-center-arena|title=Bob Seger coming to Peoria Civic Center Arena|first=Phil|last=Luciano|work=[[Journal_Star_(Peoria)|Journal Star of Peoria]]|date=2018-09-18|accessdate=2018-10-07|archive-date=2018-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007223121/http://www.pjstar.com/news/20180918/bob-seger-coming-to-peoria-civic-center-arena|dead-url=no}}</ref>席格分別於2004年和2012年入選[[搖滾名人堂|搖滾名人堂]]和{{link-en|詞曲作家名人堂|Songwriters Hall of Fame}}。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockhall.com/inductees/bob-seger/ |title=Bob Seger: inducted in 2004 | The Rock and Roll Hall of Fame and Museum |publisher=Rockhall.com |date= |accessdate=2013-08-06 |archive-date=2013-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130916111825/https://rockhall.com/inductees/bob-seger/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="rollingstone1">{{cite magazine |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/bob-seger-gordon-lightfoot-jim-steinman-inducted-into-songwriters-hall-of-fame-20120615 |title=Bob Seger, Gordon Lightfoot, Jim Steinman Inducted into Songwriters Hall of Fame | Music News |magazine=Rolling Stone |date=2012-06-15 |accessdate=2013-08-06 |archive-date=2014-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140131205822/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/bob-seger-gordon-lightfoot-jim-steinman-inducted-into-songwriters-hall-of-fame-20120615 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="billboard1">{{cite magazine |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/483079/bob-seger-gordon-lightfoot-among-songwriter-hall-inductees |title=Bob Seger, Gordon Lightfoot Among Songwriter Hall inductees |magazine=Billboard |accessdate=2013-08-06 |archive-date=2013-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130623072419/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/483079/bob-seger-gordon-lightfoot-among-songwriter-hall-inductees |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://songhall.org/news/entry/songwriters_hall_of_fame_announces_2012_inductees |title=Songwriters Hall of Fame Announces 2012 Inductees |publisher=SongHall |date= |accessdate=2013-08-06 |archive-date=2013-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022054015/http://songhall.org/news/entry/songwriters_hall_of_fame_announces_2012_inductees |dead-url=no }}</ref>席格在2018年9月宣布了自己的告別巡演。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/bob-seger-and-the-silver-bullet-band-announce-farewell-tour-725085/|title=Bob Seger and the Silver Bullet Band Announce Farewell Tour|first=Andy|last=Greene|date=2018-09-18|publisher=|accessdate=2018-10-13|archive-date=2018-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181014053035/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/bob-seger-and-the-silver-bullet-band-announce-farewell-tour-725085/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

